Go to the repo: https://github.com/polk-uh/sitemap

Click the green "Code" button and switch to the Codespaces tab

Click "Create codespace on main"

    This will create a new Codespace and open it in a new tab

Wait for it to finish setting up

In the terminal (bottom of the screen), run:
python -m pip install -r requirements.txt
python sitemap_script.py [insert the URL you want to generate a sitemap for]


The sitemap will be generated and saved as sitemap_output.xlsx in the same directory as the script.

ex: 
python -m pip install -r requirements.txt
python sitemap_script.py http://www.habitualbedemo.com/

Find sitemap_output.xlsx in the list of files.

Right-click on it.

Select "Download" from the context menu.

Itâ€™ll download to your local machine/laptop. Paste the spreadsheet contents into your MC_migration_QA_checklist_EXAMPLE.xlsx copied file.